name: Museum of the Mountain Man
address: Museum of the Mountain Man, Pinedale WY, 82941
info: This is a drive up clinic at the Mountain Man Museum.  Please wear a mask and a short sleeve shirt. For any questions, phone Public Health @ 367-2157.
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Big Horn County Public Health-Greybull
info: This will be a drive thru clinic.  Please pull up to the side door between the Senior Center and basketball/tennis court.  If the date and time doesn't work, please give our office a call.  We would be happy to work with you to accommodate your schedule.
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Sweetwater Community Nursing Services
vaccines: Janssen COVID-19 Vaccine, Pfizer-BioNTech COVID-19 Vaccine
info: Both Pfizer and J&J vaccine are available on a walk-in basis, no appointment necessary. If you do not schedule online we will help you register when you come to the office.  If you are scheduling a second dose of Pfizer, it has to be at least 17 days since your first dose, preferably closer to 21 days.  J&J vaccine does NOT require a second dose.
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Fremont County Public Health-Riverton
vaccines: Pfizer-BioNTech COVID-19 Vaccine, Moderna COVID-19 Vaccine, Janssen COVID-19 Vaccine
info: Please wear short sleeved shirts and expect to be observed for 15 minutes after your injection. If you have any anaphylactic allergies requiring use of an epi-pen in the past we will be unable to give you a vaccine, you will need to get your vaccine in a clinic or hospital. If you have any questions please call our office at 856-6979, Thank You!
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
